@host = http://127.0.0.1:18090

### 登录：admin
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 登录：operator
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator",
  "password": "op123"
}

### 登录：guest
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "guest",
  "password": "guest123"
}

### 未登录访问受保护接口（预期 401）
GET {{host}}/profile/me
